---
// src/components/FazilServices.astro
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Ofrecemos soluciones tecnológicas especializadas para impulsar tu negocio con las últimas tecnologías
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      
      <!-- API Development -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Desarrollo de APIs</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Creamos interfaces de programación robustas y escalables para conectar sistemas y aplicaciones de manera eficiente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Landing Pages -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9m0 9c-5 0-9-4-9-9s4-9 9-9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Landing Pages Optimizadas</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Desarrollamos páginas de aterrizaje de alto rendimiento optimizadas para conversión y experiencia de usuario.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Performance Optimization -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-yellow-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Optimización de Performance</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Mejoramos la velocidad y rendimiento de sitios web y aplicaciones existentes para maximizar la eficiencia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech Consulting -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Consultoría Tecnológica</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Asesoramos en la selección de tecnologías y arquitecturas más adecuadas para cada proyecto específico.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Web Development -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Desarrollo Web</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Construimos sitios web modernos y funcionales utilizando las últimas tecnologías y mejores prácticas.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Note -->
    <div class="text-center bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Información Importante</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Cotización personalizada según requerimientos técnicos</strong> - Contáctanos si quieres conocer más sobre nuestros servicios y recibir una propuesta adaptada a tu proyecto.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>